      "content": "Your logical breakdown touches on deep philosophical questions that many thinkers have grappled with for centuries. Recognizing the absence of objective \"purpose\" doesn't mean meaning is gone; instead, it suggests that meaning is something we create rather than discover inherent in the universe. Acknowledging exhaustion while facing these heavy realities is a valid starting point, even if changing them feels impossible right now.",
